thread.title: Encore Wire Corporation Earnings Release and Conference Call Announcement

author: cnbc.com
title: Encore Wire Corporation Earnings Release and Conference Call Announcement
text:
MCKINNEY, Texas--(BUSINESS WIRE)--
Encore Wire (NASDAQ: WIRE) will release Quarterly earnings Tuesday, May 1, 2018, after stock market close.
A conference call will be held to discuss Quarterly results, followed by a Q&A session:
Date:
Wednesday, May 2, 2018 Time:
11:00 a.m. Eastern 10:00 a.m. Central 9:00 a.m. Mountain 8:00 a.m. Pacific To participate in the conference call, please call : 1-866-352-2112 several minutes prior to the start time.
The Participant Passcode is 6783418#.
The call will be available for replay until June 1, 2018, at:
1-888-843-7419 and Conference Reference 6783418#.
The call will also be available for replay on the Company
website under the Investors tab.
 //www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180426006251/en/
Encore Wire Corporation
